    "synopsis": "Two parallel storylines track the Dark Angels Legion in the early days of the Heresy. In the void, Brother-Chaplain Nemiel rides with Lion El'Jonson as the primarch leads a raid on the forge world Diamat to deny vital siege weapons to Horus, learning only fragments of the wider treachery. Down on Caliban, Librarian Zahariel and the exiled Luther struggle to hold a homeworld sliding into open insurrection, while an ancient evil stirs beneath the forests of the First Legion's cradle. As loyalties fracture across two fronts, the seeds of the Lion's eventual sundering with his old friend take root, foreshadowing the catastrophe that will scatter the Dark Angels.",
